              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "288 mg of plutonium (enriched to 98.26 % in 242Pu) in",
                " a sulphur matrix. Sulphur + Pu is 2.7189 g. The",
                " target was mounted in a thin walled Al can as a slag",
                " 2.5x2.5 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To subtract contaminant lines, measurements of the",
                " background target activity prior neutron activation",
                " were performed. Off-resonance measurement at 2.040 eV",
                " was made to determine the gamma-ray lines from sulphur",
                " and other Pu isotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Contaminant gamma-ray lines were used to accurately",
                " know calibration energies below 1000 keV. These lines",
                " were supplemented by those from standard RdTh and",
                " 60Co sources as well as calibrated pulser."
              ]
            }
          ],
